## Stack

| Layer | Tech |
|---|---|
| ZK Circuit | [Noir](https://noir-lang.org) (Aztec) |
| Proof backend | Barretenberg (UltraPlonk) |
| Smart contracts | Solidity on [Base](https://base.org) |
| Frontend | Vanilla JS + `@noir-lang/noir_js` |
| Token | Soulbound ERC-721 |
